
\section{Overview}

The code in [[parser_php.mly]] is mostly a copy paste of the Yacc
parser in the PHP source code (in
[[pfff/docs/official-grammar/5.2.11/zend_language_parser.y]]) adapted
for [[ocamlyacc]].
